title: Did NYU publish a report on Clinton and Soros 'Women Paying Money to Charge Trump with Sexual Assault'?
subtitle: The fact that the New York Times article, which is actually two years old, is a blatantly offensive website.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: In fact, the New York Times reported that Hillary Clinton and George Soros were responsible for paying a woman to make false allegations of sexual abuse of Donald Trump.
